data.description: Beautiful Brick home on 4.1 acres+-. Home has 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, open floor plan with high ceilings, eat in kitchen with granite counter top, with living room. Split bedroom plan master with marble Jacuzzi tub, separate shower    with ceramic tile on the walls and floor, granite counter top, large closet, 2 bedrooms on the other side of home and a full bath, 1 bedroom upstairs. Has a large screened in porch and a separate deck, double garage. Only 15 minutes from I-55 and about 20 minutes from Olive Branch.
